title: United Kingdom Imports of Knitted Or Crocheted Fabrics
description: Imports of Knitted Or Crocheted Fabrics in the United Kingdom increased to 15.54 GBP Million in September from 11.58 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Knitted Or Crocheted Fabrics in the United Kingdom averaged 12.64 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 22.19 GBP Million in March of 2022 and a record low of 4.32 GBP Million in December of 2007. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Knitted Or Crocheted Fabrics.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
